/* T1-depth content for the 4 in-corpus Navagraha temples:           */
/*   #12 Kanjanur (Venus), #66 Thirunallar (Saturn),                 */
/*   #71 Alangudi (Jupiter), #87 Thirunageswaram (Rahu).             */
